    public class ShrgComboBox
extends javax.swing.JComboBox<java.lang.String>
    One of the gui components that takes a seat in Json tree project. It may be made to identify a sub-context of definition, that is, it may collaborate to identify the path of group of an attributes or sets of values within the Json tree. In other words it can impersonate a "selector" of context, in order to have data displayed or stored.
